32-bit display support

manual fb mode switch via command-line option

attempt auto mode switch for 16-bit (565 -> 555 to eliminate pixel repack)

ImPS/2 and USB mouse protocols

alternative keyboard maps (sucked in from /usr/share/keymaps)

clipboard

printing

mapdelbs option to enable 127 -> 8 backspace mapping

option to enable VT switch with Alt-Fn

option to find and run on a free VT rather than taking over the active one

make it play nice when launched from within X11

